Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.43,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Last Shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The climax of Mobile Suit Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,While the head is gone and it's all banged up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it muster up all of its remaining strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:28.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and shot the Zeong above it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:37.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You made this, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:39.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try and build one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:40.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:53.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Our sales is low when compared to the sales of Division 1 and 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and because of the new division that was just created
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:56.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,at this rate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:59.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Division 3 will be dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:02.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Division 3 is going to get dissolved after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about who is going to take over for Manten-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You knew about this, right Chief Inuzuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was going to tell everyone when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:16.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course Division 3 is an important place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I tried talking to the higher ups, I was not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:23.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:27.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's this COOL JAPAN competition that Asai from Division 1 looked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:30.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a big project that will be held in Singapore next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:31.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If we get this project,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,there might still be a chance that Division 3 will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No good will come with doing something unnecessary like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:38.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If there something that I can do, then I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:39.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's unlike you, Nakano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want Division 3 to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:42.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:43.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:44.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:46.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We should avoid taking risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:53.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you fine if Division 3 goes away, Saruwatari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:59.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:01.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well said, Saru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:05.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe Division 3 is on the verge of death, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,let's turn things around with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:08.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:09.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Division 3's Last Shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:17.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that? It's scary though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Our feelings became one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It takes a variety of techniques to complete Last Shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:33.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And there's no right answer when it comes to plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:36.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I head this from Shinji-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,he said that you're really busy at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is more like wishful thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:46.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's one of those moments that happen a few times in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:51.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're going to make the base kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:53.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:14.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How to present the good points of Japan to Singapore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:17.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In the past, major event companies has a stronghold on events of this magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The project is the key to stand out from the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not just introducing Japanese culture as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:30.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,how about we combine the culture of Japan and Singapore and make a hybrid presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai suggested that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was taken aback because I thought that you came up with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:41.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:50.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a legendary scene that any Gundam fan knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A miracle that was produced by the Gundam without a head and left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:57.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can see the story looking by looking at the plastic model that you built.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's build your very own Last Shooting, Zakunee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is a Master Grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:08.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because you're going to build the insides too, the amount of parts is a lot more than an old kit and a High Grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:12.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It still looks cool if you can see the insides after making modifications, that is what Master Grade is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:18.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:25.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:33.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:35.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The temporary assembly is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, now decide the parts that you want to modify.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I leave the designs of the booths to you, Kijimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The stage and ideas, also leave that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yo! Kijimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The theme is Japanese culture, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:12.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,traditionally there are Kabuki, Noh, Japanese dance, Sumo and many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But recently there are a lot of famous Japanese contents such as manga, anime, games and vtubers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Recently, Japanese foods such as {\i1}dashi{\i0} (soup stock) and {\i1}umami{\i0} (flavor) were also explored in depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:21.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was well researched.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good job, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's narrow it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:28.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I will choose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to support you, so let's do this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:36.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got the list of animation companies that we have ties to from Division 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good job, Saru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you get it from Oishi-san and Asai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The fact that they're helping us out is top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's take it up a notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You've been working all this time, you should take a rest, Zakunee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can still go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to destroy the left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is my first time seeing someone build Last Shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Use the nipper and go wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's even harder than doing it meticulously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:26.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:40.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the correct response.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:46.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You now love plastic models, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:50.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So your heart rejects the fact that you're going to destroy it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is my wishful thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's already late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for staying here until this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go home and sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:08:59.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please check this, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Chief, can I ask you to do the presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:11.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Should I use a pomade for the first time in a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because the animation company needs a little bit more of a push, I'm going to go see them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:18.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:20.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:23.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I really want for Division 3 to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no other division as kind as Division 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the most comfortable place in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's fight to protect the most comfortable place in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:34.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's nearly time to clock out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What can we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:43.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about praying for the presentation to succeed and have fish and {\i1}sake{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:44.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're going to start the painting process today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next up is put on some ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Add shadows to create a three-dimensional effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next, use the gray ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:41.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next up is weathering the damaged parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Weathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:09.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imagine just what kind of adventures that this thing has gone trough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the goal is to get close to what we have in mind as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:16.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is truly the ultimate imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Finally, use the matting spray as the topcoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can see the what it's going to look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We can finally see the light at the end of the tunnel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You won't get any strength if you only eat salad, Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't have an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you get enough sleep, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You've already talked to the general manager about this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's quite a large budget proposal, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, this wont pass the internal review.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My intention is to push this trough, even if it means my head is on the chopping block.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:23.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's a chance that you might be fired and not get the green light, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:29.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:31.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:33.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It seems like she's really busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that from Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's about Division 3, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything about it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to completely turn the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great that we got to dream for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:27.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry about not thinking about your position, Chief Inuzuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have thought about it without sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if I failed spectacularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to show everyone a cool side of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show you what a man of the Showa era is made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if you fail spectacularly, It will only be traumatic for your subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Reiwa is not even going to let me go out spectacularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no need for someone to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:14:00.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got the assurance from the President that we'll get the permission to participate in this competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's my colleague after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're so amazing, Acting Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,To be honest, my resolve is up in the air, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's all lift Kijimura up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get back to work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:16.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:21.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I leave it to you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do I look okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:49.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You look perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Chief Inuzuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gunpla?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is a scene called Last Shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the one that you said the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:58.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Now you can settle it once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm entrusting you with this, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This doesn't have a head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is the implication that I'm the only one who's going to get fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:19.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:32.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I am honored to participate in the presentation of this very important event to introduce Japanese culture to the people of Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:38.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not just Japanese culture like Kabuki, anime, vtubers, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,we will also incorporate the culture of Singapore
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and create an unprecedented event space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And lastly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:53.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I believe our company can create the best event possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:05.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think only you could have done it, Inuzuka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:06.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want everyone to lift you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:21.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The things that I learned here, is my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There are lots to do in HR.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show that I can become a Gundam here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:48.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's share a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was fun working with everyone in Division 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:18.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We got heated, that was so unlike us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even though we're going to be on different divisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:30.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,let's do our very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was surprised by just how much relaxed Division 3 is when I first joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:37.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was a bit more on edge when I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even though everyone went along with my proposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was all to protect the most comfortable place on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I will fight for that sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:04.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nobody forced us to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:26.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The gap between me and everyone has shrunk because of plastic models and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,"I made such a face".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got to know a lot of different sides of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,More than I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Division 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:36.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I got attatched to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't sort out my feelings right now though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm over 40 and still can't understand my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:20:00.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My Last Shooting with everyone failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm so frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:12.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't it your First Shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:27.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can still see Oishi-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Youth is a right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if you fail, don't regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is no data that says it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do it for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai RIko, is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:58.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:16.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Will you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:06.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you got rejected, Zakunee?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What should I build next?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:10.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did he tell you that he only sees you as a little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:11.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've made my mind up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you going to build?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:14.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Himeji castle and Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:15.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A collaboration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:17.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do anything with plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:18.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:21.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy, so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:24.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,